153
00:08:51,711 --> 00:08:54,509
- Look, what's your name?
- My name's Rupert Pupkin.

154
00:08:54,581 --> 00:08:58,312
All right.
Look, pal, got to tell you,
this is a crazy business...

155
00:08:58,384 --> 00:09:00,875
but it's not unlike any other business.
There are ground rules.

156
00:09:00,954 --> 00:09:02,819
Yeah.

157
00:09:02,889 --> 00:09:06,325
And you don't just walk
onto a network show
without experience.

158
00:09:06,392 --> 00:09:08,826
Now, I know it's
an old hackneyed expression...

159
00:09:08,895 --> 00:09:11,887
but it's the truth--
you've got to start at the bottom.

160
00:09:11,965 --> 00:09:15,059
- I'm at the bottom.
- That's a perfect place to start.

161
00:09:15,134 --> 00:09:17,659
I know, but I'm not--
there's got to be--

162
00:09:17,737 --> 00:09:20,331
It looks so simple
to the viewer at home--

163
00:09:20,406 --> 00:09:23,341
those things that come
so easily that are so relaxed...

164
00:09:23,409 --> 00:09:26,344
and look like it's a matter
of just taking another breath.

165
00:09:26,412 --> 00:09:28,846
It takes years
and years and years...

166
00:09:28,915 --> 00:09:30,849
of honing that and working it.

167
00:09:30,917 --> 00:09:32,851
I don't mean to interrupt you...

168
00:09:32,919 --> 00:09:35,319
